sbm(N, k)

sbm: Construct a stochastic block model

Args: N (integer): Graph size k (integer): Number of clusters pij (float): Probability of intercluster edges pii (float): probability of intracluster edges

Returns: A (numpy.array): Adjacency matrix gt (numpy.array): Ground truth cluster labels coords(numpy.array): plotting coordinates for the sbm
